{"tid":168231,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"K1工作紙動物配對超難 朱千雪搲頭：諗唔到邏輯關係","createTime":"2017-03-23T11:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T13:49:17.000Z","uid":9573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"498ec5b741cc4bd3bbcdb06602836ba416613b82","tid":168231,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"香港家長最愛說「贏在起跑線」，由幼稚園開始已經力谷小朋友的功課學業，還未計一大籮的興趣班，小朋友為滿足父母的期望疲於奔命。近日網上瘋傳一份K1的功課，要將左右兩組動物圖案配成一對，咪以為K1功課好容易，擁有碩士學歷的港姐朱千雪試玩後，只能說出各個動物圖案的英文字，至於美國大學畢業的簡淑兒只是撞中一題，還有廖子妤、Super Girls也被小兒科功課難倒，在起跑線已經脫腳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/482883/xlarge/5143288f857bdf4ba8998a0416f1e7d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F482883%2Fxlarge%2F5143288f857bdf4ba8998a0416f1e7d8.jpg&h=d9a3935d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳的K1功課，卻難倒了不少大人。<br />\n<br />\n朱千雪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4219D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4219D.jpg&h=d01f36cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港姐朱千雪擁有碩士學歷，正在城大攻讀法律博士，在圈中一直被譽為才女，但她看到這份K1功課，也一樣無從入手，不過英文底子甚佳的她，很快已寫出每種動物的英文，但兩者如何相連卻無從入手，她表示：「我K1嘅時候肯定唔識做，我一直都唔算好聰明。我只係識得啲字，但唔知點有邏輯地配對，諗唔到邏輯關係。」<br />\n<br />\n簡淑兒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqF34kp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvqF34kp.jpg&h=5dd97a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在美國讀大學的簡淑兒，在嘗試做這份K1功課時解釋：「鹿好溫馴，蟻都唔會踩死隻，唔會傷害人，所以是同一類。狗狗同bear bear係人類最好朋友，狗仔又好忠心，好多人都鍾意，又會攬住bear bear瞓，狗仔同bear bear係一對。至於貓同駱駝都係可以同人類做到朋友，但貓有時會發下小脾氣，駱駝都係。而老虎同鱷魚一樣，最好唔好接近佢，唔知幾時會噬你一啖。」總算是答中一題。<br />\n<br />\n廖子妤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h16wu24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh16wu24.jpg&h=0df83ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影《骨妹》的女主角廖子妤，則毫無頭緒，反問記者「熊bear bear係動物？(teddy同tiger有乜關係？)因為T？」在記者提示下，她隨即以deer配dog，ant配alligator，cat配camel。她笑說「我好慶幸我已經長大咗，真係好難。」<br />\n<br />\nSuper Girls<br />\n<br />\nSuper Girls的Cheronna、Yanny及Jessica，對這份功課議論紛紛，不斷商量，Jessica表示：「我諗係屬性，即係咩科對咩科。」Yanny則說bear bear要配狗仔，因為好似。Jessica更說螞蟻可以配恐龍，隨即被Cheronna更正「鱷魚嚟的，所以應該老虎配鱷魚，因為都係食肉嘅。」Jessica則反駁：「狗同貓都食肉啦。」三人你一言我一語，最後也是亂撞居多，當然是全軍覆沒。在知道答案後更不約而同O晒嘴，一臉無奈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/482790/xlarge/19240c103517dbd6c151ecd412421bbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F482790%2Fxlarge%2F19240c103517dbd6c151ecd412421bbc.jpg&h=4a52724c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSuper Girls知悉答案後，全部O晒嘴。<br />\n<br />\n正確答案：<br />\n<br />\ntiger、teddy<br />\n<br />\ndog、deer<br />\n<br />\nant、alligator<br />\n<br />\ncat、camel"},{"pid":"25b4872878a20726e66777f31f2f036deb37c041","tid":168231,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p9dk5yDaai0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp9dk5yDaai0&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d0838627\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p9dk5yDaai0</a>"},{"pid":"a02f0d49a932ef83aea2c17746102c4afd2343fc","tid":168231,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"睇post估樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34363ba6cc15e94fbea2a7d12a58e022f49c1d80","tid":168231,"uid":20640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:58:21.000Z","msg":"好想奶爆千雪個加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd756c7c3d854ceab6fc4491b1622d20f4c28962","tid":168231,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"份野係咪cut頭cut尾呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020fbbe80d61c85ecbb27ce3e0c356458e42e866","tid":168231,"uid":27519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"點解全部都係千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f25d84f901a505b3b34608e74543a98dcde6fee","tid":168231,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:02:40.000Z","msg":"簡淑兒答得咁弱智"},{"pid":"66b89aee448f5b65583bc30b31bb157ffa778dd2","tid":168231,"uid":91981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"淨係知teddy bear係隻公仔 ，乜而家Teddy 係等於bear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd5e01433c6c125238f9e91978f48ab7582121f","tid":168231,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡淑兒答得咁弱智</blockquote><br />\n直情係幽默"},{"pid":"68f592085469117e01a65fd43c4dc822b9acf674","tid":168231,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"都白痴, K1 啲小朋友連裏面所有動物都未必識得哂"},{"pid":"de5c9a342c4d9737182a6a423ead5da469546bd4","tid":168231,"uid":14191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>簡淑兒答得咁弱智</blockquote><br />\n直情係幽默</blockquote><br />\n佢真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對眼又好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"2e3121ace4fef742321a74cb35d5baf8759d0482","tid":168231,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>簡淑兒答得咁弱智</blockquote><br />\n直情係幽默</blockquote><br />\n佢真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對眼又好撚恐怖</blockquote><br />\n屌晒你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae558f8b2871f053022c6412fd59f1b5a3ac112b","tid":168231,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"千雪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lom